[21/01/2017 12:05:32] <font color="#ffffff">(CUENTA ATR S)</font>
[21/01/2017 12:05:43] <font color="#00ffff">Y a través</font>
[21/01/2017 12:05:43] <font color="#00ffff">de esas galaxias y estrellas,</font>
