[21/01/2017 20:25:34] <font color="#ff00ff">No.</font>
[21/01/2017 20:25:37] <font color="#ffffff">Ven.</font>
[21/01/2017 20:25:39] <font color="#ffffff">Entonces ven.</font>
[21/01/2017 20:25:47] <font color="#ffffff">Estoy aquí.</font>
[21/01/2017 20:25:50] <font color="#ffffff">No te preocupes.</font>
[21/01/2017 20:26:00] <font color="#ffffff">-¿Qué, comisario?</font>
[21/01/2017 20:26:00] <font color="#ffffff">¿Ha liberado a su querida mamá?</font>
[21/01/2017 20:26:02] <font color="#ffffff">La principal sospechosa.</font>
